import React from 'react'
import CommonSection from '../shared/CommonSection'

import '../styles/tours.css';
import tourData from '../assets/data/tours'
import TourCard from '../shared/data/TourCard';
import SearchBar from '../shared/data/SearchBar'
import Newslettert from '../shared/data/Newsletter'

const Tours = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <CommonSection title={'All Tours'} />
    <section>
      <Container>
        <Row>
          <SearchBar />
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </section>
    </>
  )
}

export default Tours
